Installing Happy ABC on a Unix machine
======================================

PREREQUISITES
-------------

* ocaml 3.10 or latter
* omake
* findlib
* extlib
* xml-light
* oUnit(for unit test)

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
-------------------------

If you type:

   $ omake all
   $ (omake check)
   $ (sudo) omake install

then install to a default directory(/usr/local/).

Or,install to another directory:

   $ omake all
   $ (omake check)
   $ (sudo) omake install PREFIX=/path/to/

